(142, '<p>Satsuma Bowl</p>\r\r\n', '1322805600', '0000-00-00', 'C 1880', '0', '0', '0', '0', '5500', 0, 'No', '99', '<p>This bowl is painted with a central panel of Kian Yin and attendants surrounded with a continuous scene of boys, the outside painted with a continuous scene of immortals and attendants.</p>\r\r\n', '', '0', 'GBP', 'GBP', 'Shelf 11', 'A', '', '<p>Fine Japanese Satsuma bowl painted with a central panel of Kuan Yin and attendants surrounded with a continuous scene of boys, the outside painted with a continuous scene of immortals and attendants, signed Seikozan, Meiji period, c 1880. (wood st', 'Active', '', '0', '', '', '', '', 'Yes'),
