(631, '<p>3 Piece Tea set</p>\r\r\n', '1366693200', '0000-00-00', 'C 1913', '0', '0', '0', '0', '90', 0, 'No', 'A79', '<p>Shallow three piece tea set with teapot, creamer and sugar bowl. The items have embossed detailing on the corners and ball feet.<br />\r\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\r\n', '', '0', 'GBP', 'GBP', 'None Assigned', 'Q', '<p>John Lawrence &amp; Co. registered 1813 in Birmingham.</p>\r\r\n', '', 'Inactive', 'Sold', '99', 'GBP', 'Newby Singapore', '', '', 'No'),
